Package: shapeshifter
Version: 2.0.1
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libgtk-3-0, libfontconfig1, libxcb-render0, libxcb-shape0, libxcb-xfixes0, libxkbcommon0, libssl3
Maintainer: Shapeshifter Dev <developer@lilith-linux.org>
Description: Desktop Environment & Profile Manager for Lilith Linux
 Shapeshifter unifies desktop environment switching, profile management,
 and system configuration backup into a single native application.
 Features include profile create/apply/export/import, DE switching with
 conflict prevention, backup item management, folder backup, and
 automatic profile saving.

